# CVE-2026-33811
# Category: other
# Rationale: Go stdlib net (LookupCNAME w/ cgo resolver) — embedded in /usr/bin/gh (GitHub CLI 2.92.0 built with Go 1.26.2). Fixed in Go 1.25.10 / 1.26.3; resolution requires upstream cli/cli to rebuild and republish the apt package. No newer gh release available in cli.github.com/packages/dists/stable as of 2026-05-16.
# Exploitability: none — vessel does not invoke gh against attacker-controlled hostnames; CNAME lookup path requires malicious DNS responses.
# Expires: 2026-08-14
# Reviewer: @mvillmow  PR #662
CVE-2026-33811

# CVE-2026-33814
# Category: other
# Rationale: Go stdlib HTTP/2 SETTINGS frame infinite loop — embedded in /usr/bin/gh (GitHub CLI 2.92.0 built with Go 1.26.2). Fixed in Go 1.25.10 / 1.26.3; requires upstream cli/cli rebuild.
# Exploitability: low — gh only connects to api.github.com (trusted upstream); no attacker-controlled HTTP/2 server in the vessel runtime context.
# Expires: 2026-08-14
# Reviewer: @mvillmow  PR #662
CVE-2026-33814

